<paragraph blockId="31.[136,1451,770,905]" pageId="31" pageNumber="242">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[189,294,806,832]" pageId="31" pageNumber="242">Notes:—</emphasis>
This species is similar to 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Kuntze" authorityYear="1891" baseAuthorityName="Lindl." box="[576,683,806,832]" class="Liliopsida" family="Orchidaceae" genus="Humboltia" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Plantae" order="Asparagales" pageId="31" pageNumber="242" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="affinis">
<emphasis box="[576,683,806,832]" italics="true" pageId="31" pageNumber="242">M. affinis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
and 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Luer" authorityYear="1982" baseAuthorityName="Barbosa Rodrigues" baseAuthorityYear="1882" box="[737,951,806,832]" class="Liliopsida" family="Orchidaceae" genus="Myoxanthus" kingdom="Plantae" order="Asparagales" pageId="31" pageNumber="242" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="parahybunensis">
<emphasis box="[737,951,806,832]" italics="true" pageId="31" pageNumber="242">M. parahybunensis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, but 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Luer &amp; Dodson" authorityYear="1992" box="[1007,1109,806,832]" class="Liliopsida" family="Orchidaceae" genus="Myoxanthus" kingdom="Plantae" order="Asparagales" pageId="31" pageNumber="242" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="neillii">
<emphasis box="[1007,1109,806,832]" italics="true" pageId="31" pageNumber="242">M. neillii</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
is distinguished from these by its small flowers with sepals only 
<quantity box="[520,613,842,869]" metricMagnitude="-3" metricUnit="m" metricValue="4.5" metricValueMax="5.0" metricValueMin="4.0" pageId="31" pageNumber="242" unit="mm" value="4.5" valueMax="5.0" valueMin="4.0">4–5 mm</quantity>
long, oblong petals not narrowed above the middle and column with teeth at the apex. Since the 
<typeStatus box="[382,480,878,904]" pageId="31" pageNumber="242">holotype</typeStatus>
at MO was not located, a 
<typeStatus box="[774,877,878,904]" pageId="31" pageNumber="242">lectotype</typeStatus>
is designated here.
</paragraph>
